<h2>How to Play Loto 6 from 45</h2>
<p>
    In Loto 6 from 45, players select 6 unique numbers from a pool ranging from 1 to 45.
    During the drawing, 6 winning numbers are drawn randomly. To win, a player's numbers
    must match the drawn numbers according to the rules of the specific prize tiers.
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Select 6 distinct numbers from 1 to 45.</li>
    <li>Matching all 6 numbers wins the jackpot.</li>
    <li>Matching fewer numbers can win lower-tier prizes.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How to Play Loto 7 from 39</h2>
<p>
    In Loto 7 from 39, players pick 7 unique numbers from a set of numbers between 1 and 39.
    The lottery draws 7 numbers, and prize tiers depend on how many matching numbers a player gets.
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Choose 7 distinct numbers from 1 to 39.</li>
    <li>Matching all 7 numbers wins the jackpot.</li>
    <li>Other prize tiers exist for fewer matches.</li>
